title: Lowest unemployment among highly educated
description: In 2016, Tajikistan had one of the lowest unemployment rates for individuals with advanced education, at just 0.241% of the total labor force with advanced education.

title: Lowest rate of child marriage by age 15
description: As of 2017, only 0.1% of women aged 20-24 in Tajikistan were first married by age 15, indicating one of the lowest rates of child marriage in the world.

title: Highest binding coverage for all products
description: In 2021, Tajikistan achieved a 100% binding coverage for all products, indicating full commitment to trade agreements.

title: Highest binding coverage for primary products
description: Tajikistan also reached 100% binding coverage for primary products in 2021, showcasing its strong adherence to trade commitments.

title: Lowest domestic credit provided by financial sector
description: In 2023, domestic credit provided by the financial sector in Tajikistan was only 11.31% of GDP, one of the lowest percentages globally.

title: Lowest investment in transport with private participation
description: In 2022, Tajikistan had one of the lowest investments in transport with private participation, amounting to just $4.5 million.

title: Lowest public-private partnership investment in transport
description: Tajikistan's investment in transport through public-private partnerships was also very low in 2022, at $4.5 million.
